title: Randy Brecker (and Mike Stern!) Interview with Ed Sax School - Part 1/5
description:
For more interviews, free video lessons, backing tracks and handouts, come to http://edsaxschool.com.

Ed Barker, soloist for George Michael and founder of Ed Sax School, interviews international trumpet star, Grammy Award winning RANDY BRECKER (with an entertaining intervention by guitar legend, MIKE STERN!).
